snippet.textDisplay:
Favourite moments:

00:12 When you look at them...when you get to know CS dint limit themselves to the voices of just two genders.
00:19 his hand gestures... 00:23 and the bhangra type step here.. :-P
00:32 That Dhol coming along...
00:41 their step... and this tappa is already so entertaining..
00:59 and they look so motherly here...
01:18 at first you don't know how much this "thaaaah" you're going to like...
01:24 his hand gestures...we know he's enjoying so much..
01:49 aren't his hand gestures adorable? I love the video of this song.
01:57 Impeccable high notes... 02:00 those gestures enhancing the effects of magic in his voice..
02:17 Yeh urr jayenge bhai aj... :-D
02:23 Baalkada lines...always give me goosebumps..the most enjoyable part of this song...
02:37 Jimmy khan... we need to learn some of your gestures...
03:04 The arrangement is so freaking good here...seems like something out of their voice initiated that instrument...like cannonballs shooted out of the cannons...and the camera suddenly starts focusing on those cannonballs..
03:08 - - - - Those lines...heartwrenching..
03:23 Who wants to join "Jimmy Khan Hand Gestures' Club"?
03:25 Shahab Hussain certainly won't stop. 03:27 so will Jimmy Khan... 
03:30 and they won't stop soaring...
03:36 those sudden high notes give me an ample amount of satisfaction..with baalkada being sung along... 
04:00 Thanks for doing that... :-P

One of the very few songs I've liked from this season... Keep up the good work... :-)
